# Tabs UI Project

Interactive tabs component built with HTML, CSS and Vanilla JavaScript.

## ---Description

This project demonstrates how to create a dynamic tabs interface where:

- Each tab changes the background color.
- Each tab updates the displayed content.
- Only the selected tab shows an active bottom border.
- The active state switches when another tab is clicked.

The project focuses on DOM manipulation, event handling, and dynamic class management using pure JavaScript.


## 🚀 How to Run the Project

1. Download or clone the repository.
2. Open the project folder.
3. Double-click on `tabs.html`.

OR

Right-click `tabs.html` → Open with your browser.

No installation or dependencies required.

